taxonomy: N. pachyderma assumed to be right-coiling (because southerly location and fact that for the northern trap (WCT2) this is explicitly mentioned) and changed to incompta. G_quadrilobatus merged with sacculifer
remarks: total shell flux and species fluxes reported in paper are not always consistent perhaps because of size fraction issues. Depth change
